🔹 Procedure Question

❓ Write a procedure to accept value of m and n and display the total count of odd numbers from m to n.


---

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE count_odd(m INT, n INT)
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
DECLARE
    i INT;
    cnt INT := 0;
BEGIN
    FOR i IN m..n LOOP
        IF i % 2 <> 0 THEN
            cnt := cnt + 1;
        END IF;
    END LOOP;

    RAISE NOTICE 'Total Odd Numbers = %', cnt;
END;
$$;


---

✅ Call

